request.description:
Returns the liveness status of the API, PostgreSQL, and Redis.

**Auth:** None required.

**200 — all services healthy:**
```json
{
  "status": "ok",
  "version": "0.0.1",
  "env": "development",
  "services": {
    "database": "ok",
    "redis": "ok"
  }
}
```

**503 — one or more services degraded:**
```json
{
  "status": "degraded",
  "services": {
    "database": "error",
    "redis": "ok"
  }
}
```
